Key Match Events: Kiril Despodov scored the only goal of the match in the 40th minute.
Dan Ballard's header from the center of the box missed to the left in the 90'+6' minute.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was held at Hristo Botev Stadium, Plovdiv with an attendance of 14,300.
The referee for the match was Anastasios Sidiropoulos.
